Distribution. Widely distributed throughout the Goldfields region of Western Australia (
Fig. 1
). From just outside the south-eastern edge of the Pilbara, then south to near Norseman. Two older western records are from Yalgoo ( WAM
R 13639
) and Dongara ( WAM
R 13476
), although the latter record is likely in error given the habitat preferences of this species. A recent eastern record ( WAM R 163342 ) is from Neale Junction towards the South Australian border.
